      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 6
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# AI Memory System Health Dashboard\n\n**Purpose:** Infrastructure health monitoring - answering \"Are services healthy?\", \"How big are collections?\", \"Is deduplication working?\"\n\n**Audience:** SREs, DevOps, Capacity Planning\n\n**Services:** Qdrant (vector DB) | Embedding Service | Prometheus | Pushgateway | Grafana | Classifier Worker\n\n**Collections:** code-patterns (HOW) | conventions (WHAT) | discussions (WHY)\n\n\n**Template Variables:** Use dropdown above to filter by project (group_id)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Qdrant Status",
      "description": "**Metric:** `up{job=\"qdrant\"}`\n**Measures:** Qdrant service health (1=up, 0=down)\n**Expected:** Always 1 (up)\n**Action:** If 0, check docker compose, restart qdrant container\n**See:** docker/docker-compose.yml (qdrant service)",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6,
        "w": 4,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"qdrant\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Qdrant"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "DOWN",
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "DOWN",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "UP",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "#F2495C"
              },
              {
                "value": 1,
                "color": "#73BF69"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
